data.description: Welcome home to this stunning two-story home nestled in Sterling Green. Inside, you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a convenient half bathroom on the main level. The 1536 square feet of living space provides ample room for you to relax and unwind. The kitchen is  completely remodeled with beautiful wood cabinetry and offers sleek stainless steel appliances. There are 2 pantries for extra storage. The inviting front porch welcomes you home, while the full unfinished basement and additional storage throughout the house ensure you have space for all your belongings. There is updated flooring in every room, and a large living room with a cozy gas fireplace. The two-car attached garage provides convenience, and there is an 11 x 50 extended driveway. The patio and fenced-in backyard create an oasis for outdoor enjoyment. This property is truly a gem!   It's conveniently located right across the street from Sterling Green Park.
